text: The Oireachtas is the national parliament of Ireland. There are three parts of the Oireachtas: *The President of Ireland *Dáil Éireann - The lower house. It is similar to the House of Commons in the United Kingdom or the House of Representatives in the United States. *Seanad Éireann - The upper house. It is similar to the House of Lords and the Senate Only the Irish names are used, never the English Category:Politics of Ireland Category:Government of the Republic of Ireland Ireland Ireland
title: Oireachtas
